    <h1>Engagement Bait</h1>
    <p class="description">Content designed to <strong>manipulate users into interacting</strong> through hollow prompts — "Like if you agree!", "Tag 3 friends!" — rather than genuine value. Platforms have penalised these tactics since 2017 and suppress posts algorithmically.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
